About

Hello! I am a passionate and skilled full-stack web developer, proficient in various technologies essential for modern web development. My expertise lies in crafting creative and efficient solutions across both the front-end and back-end. With a strong foundation in software engineering and computer science, I bring creativity, precision, and efficiency to every project I undertake.

What I Do

Full-Stack Web Development
I excel in crafting end-to-end solutions, turning ideas into fully functional web applications. From designing engaging user interfaces to implementing robust server-side logic, I strive to create seamless and enjoyable user experiences.
Software Engineering and Computer Science
As a Software Engineer with a strong foundation in Computer Science, I've honed my skills in developing robust, scalable applications. My understanding of algorithms, data structures, and software design principles allows me to craft efficient and maintainable code, ensuring optimal performance and reliability. My experience extends to various programming languages, including Java and C++, enabling me to tackle diverse projects and domains effectively. I continually strive to stay updated with emerging technologies, leveraging this knowledge to build innovative solutions and contribute to the ever-evolving field of software engineering.

Education

2024

I am dedicated to advancing my education. 2024, I am diligently studying and preparing in parallel for my 'Licence Bac+3 in Artificial Intelligence and Data Engineering' at the 'Faculté des Sciences de l'Université Ibn-Tofail'. This pursuit is a testament to my commitment to staying at the forefront of cutting-edge technologies, particularly in the realm of Artificial Intelligence and Data Engineering. I am eager to bridge the gap between theory and practical application, leveraging my academic endeavors to enhance my contributions to the world of web development and beyond.

2023

I obtained my Bac+2 degree (Diplôme Universitaire de Technologie - DUT) from the "Ecole Supérieure de Technologie Kenitra" as a Higher Technician in Computer Engineering. During this program, I acquired a solid understanding of various essential concepts, including:

  • Proficiency in design methods and programming languages for software application development.
  • Theoretical and practical knowledge covering the entire lifecycle of software applications.
  • Expertise in the design, implementation, and management of computer networks.
  • In-depth understanding and hands-on experience in various areas, such as network setup and configuration, network administration and security, as well as telecommunications system analysis.

These experiences have equipped me with a strong foundation in the field of computer engineering, enabling me to approach new challenges with confidence and proficiency.

2021

I successfully completed my Baccalauréat in 2021 from 'Lycée Al-Wifaq' with a focus on scientific studies, particularly in physics. Opting for the science track, I immersed myself in the intriguing realm of physics. I proudly achieved a 'mention Bien' (distinction), reflecting my dedication and hard work during my years in high school. This educational journey laid a robust foundation for my subsequent academic and professional pursuits, nurturing my passion for science and fostering critical thinking skills.

Experince

2023

I undertook a comprehensive 4-month internship with IT ADVISOR Développement, where I played a crucial role in the development of a web application for sharing recipes. This involved utilizing Spring Boot and Angular to construct a microservices-based architecture with enhanced security measures, providing an invaluable opportunity to expand my skills in Full Stack Web Development.

2022

I engaged in a compelling 2-month internship focused on the development of a Java-based desktop application at INRA Kénitra. This experience was pivotal in my journey as a developer as I delved into the intricacies of creating a robust application for managing attendance, sharpening my skills in Java development and the nuances of desktop applications.

My expertise lies in crafting creative and efficient solutions across both the front-end and back-end. With a strong foundation in software engineering and computer science, I bring creativity, precision, and efficiency to every project I undertake.
